inline image descriptions

00:45:15.240 --> 00:45:17.820
in the body versus using
the alt text feature.

00:45:17.820 --> 00:45:18.900
>> SANDI: OK.

00:45:18.900 --> 00:45:23.340
so I am not a social-media expert,
guru, or user for that matter.

00:45:23.340 --> 00:45:23.770
[chuckles]

00:45:23.770 --> 00:45:25.590
So not my area of expertise.

00:45:26.780 --> 00:45:31.500
